thread.title: Henry Dixon
thread.title_full: Kiwi Drug reviewed by Henry Dixon

author: Henry Dixon
title: Henry Dixon
text:
Could not get these tablets anywhere in the UK,(no thanks to an EU edict)
Saw them advertised on the net in New Zealand of all places so I ordered
them very easy to do,they arrived on time.
The service was good, the price was comparable to the local chemist
when they were available a few years back so what more can you want?
I served alongside the ANZACS in KOREA in1952 so I knew in my opinion
anything from NZ would be OK
kind regards Henry Dixon
